{"tid":1057443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"180 萬名中國女性個人資料外洩　包括是否「Breed Ready」","createTime":"2019-03-12T01:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T02:43:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"85fb89e1ab2cd5fadbff487826737665a498af9b","tid":1057443,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/breed-10_Z7eIH_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbreed-10_Z7eIH_1200x0.png&h=4d3175c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前踢爆深圳人臉識別技術公司懷疑受中國政府資助，監控新疆穆斯林，並發現有大量中國網民私人聊天紀錄被儲存的荷蘭技術員 Victor Gevers，再爆出有超過 180 萬名中國女性的個人資料在網上外洩，包括她們的電話號碼、地址和她們是否「Breed Ready」等資訊。<br />\n<br />\nVictor Gevers 在 twitter 公布這次在網上發現的個人資料，並附有截圖；他表示相信是因為中國女性人口不足，所以有機構開始建立資料庫，紀錄超過 180 萬女性的個人資料，當中年紀最細的 15 歲。<br />\n<br />\n而被界定為「Breed Ready」的女性最細的 18 歲，而這些女性全部都是單身、已離婚或是寡婦，約 8 成住在北京。目前不肯定「Breed Ready」是意指已經生育，抑或有生育能力的女士，亦不知道這些個人資料是否來自交友程式或政府部門。<br />\n<br />\n接連踢爆中國個人資料外洩問題，Victor Gevers 回應《衛報》時表示，目前最重要的是盡快令這些資料受到保護。又表示正嘗試聯絡資料外洩的受害者，了解她們是否知情。《衛報》又引述中國網友猜測，Victor Gevers 今次發現的個人資料，可能和中國交友網站「世紀佳緣」有關，這網站的資料庫 2015 年曾被入侵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/180-萬名中國女性個人資料外洩-包括是否-breed-ready/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F180-%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6-breed-ready%2F&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6BVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=ccdaad26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F180-%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6-breed-ready%2F&h=39979726\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/180-萬名中國女性個人資料外洩-包括是否-breed-ready/</a>"},{"pid":"abba7b6732b49c89737ad8431e60e2fc0c7ac84b","tid":1057443,"uid":173849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:40:21.000Z","msg":"Breedy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e0656200a0bc004e8cf4379b633133b50f3d39","tid":1057443,"uid":135689,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高官menu<br />\n本地慰安婦"},{"pid":"82a0f182a7818c7581bfefb6d234010d6659fb73","tid":1057443,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"其實係 Breed Ready 既唔要<br />\n<br />\n方便好用"},{"pid":"41c47d1f603ca9abc1b03d7f5691423dd422f9a3","tid":1057443,"uid":116688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"規劃生育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fef59bf1b6f238b30fd9b251b3d283f12dc1ef4","tid":1057443,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇處女名單？"},{"pid":"e2b6f2393fc543c193ee14d184429ec5fc14e626","tid":1057443,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"支那網友猜測應該無錯"},{"pid":"e65770feb3008c0d99efc8819b6988425de6487e","tid":1057443,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D1PoiGEW0Ak9gzI?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD1PoiGEW0Ak9gzI%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=0f404f24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89cd238f3a88b7ace9aa3377b40370bcca2d676d","tid":1057443,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b6f2393fc543c193ee14d184429ec5fc14e626","tid":1057443,"uid":57376,"like"